RES_1_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/KANYE_WEST_VULTURES_1_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/KANYE_WEST_VULTURES_1_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/KANYE_WEST_VULTURES_1_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/KANYE_WEST_VULTURES_1_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/KANYE_WEST_VULTURES_1_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>经过长时间的拖延， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">Kanye West</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-dolla-ign">Ty Dolla $ign</a>终于发行了他们备受争议的新合作专辑“Vultures 1”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/kanye-west-white-lives-matter-unforgivable-opinion-3323984"><b>凭借“白人的命也是命”的绝技，坎耶·维斯特终于到了无可挽回的地步吗？</b></a></li></ul><p>几个月来，两人一直在戏弄他们的新专辑，此前有消息于 2023 年 8 月首次传出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-reportedly-preparing-to-drop-new-music-imminently-3490252">，West 将“立即”发行新音乐</a>，随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-ty-dolla-signs-vulture-album-release-date-when-3569178">有报道称将于 1 月底发行</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/another-new-release-date-set-for-kanye-west-and-ty-dolla-igns-vultures-3572393">发布日期定于昨天</a>（2 月 9 日星期五）。</p><p>当这一目标未能实现时，许多人预计会无限期等待。然而，这张唱片（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-shares-dramatic-vultures-trailer-releases-dates-three-volumes-new-music-3575720">三张专辑中的第一张</a>）现已在<a href="https://music.apple.com/mx/album/vultures-1/1730186010?l=en-GB" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple Music</a> 、 <a href="https://music.amazon.com/albums/B0CVF1RD2K" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon Music</a> 、 <a href="https://tidal.com/browse/album/344769289" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TIDAL</a>和<a href="https://open.spotify.com/album/0k7ALIqqds5oGFtpMsaHLK?si=081aa680e9cf4c46" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Spotify</a>上发行。在到达后者之前有一些延迟，导致许多人相信它可能会在该平台上可用。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：VULTURES 1" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/0k7ALIqqds5oGFtpMsaHLK?si=081aa680e9cf4c46&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>这张包含 16 首曲目的专辑还包括 Lil Durk、Bump J、Freddie Gibbs、Playboi Carti、Travis Scott、Quavo 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-daughter-north-to-make-rap-debut-on-new-song-3558914">West 的女儿 North</a>的贡献。查看下面的曲目列表。</p><p> 1.“明星”<br /> 2.《我生命的钥匙》<br /> 3.“付费”<br /> 4.“说话”<br /> 5.《回到我身边》<br /> 6.“胡德拉特”<br /> 7.“做吧”<br /> 8.“文书工作”<br /> 9.“燃烧”<br /> 10.“操萨姆”<br /> 11.《秃鹫》（浩劫版）<br /> 12.“嘉年华”<br /> 13.“请求宽恕”<br /> 14.“好（别死）”<br /> 15.“有问题”<br /> 16.《国王》</p><p>韦斯特通过分享这幅艺术作品宣布了此次发布，该艺术作品似乎展示了他身着全黑、戴着曲棍球面具的样子，他的妻子比安卡·森索里 (Bianca Censori) 也裸体加入其中。</p><p>韦斯特因分享妻子裸体或暴露服装的照片而受到批评——System <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/system-of-a-downs-john-dolmayan-tells-kanye-west-show-some-class-man-3567248">Of A Down 鼓手约翰·多尔马扬 (John Dolmayan) 告诉他要“表现出一些风度</a>”，并补充道：“你的妻子不应该成为你的战利品，她是你的骄傲和尊严的地方。这不是办法”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3LB7LeO5FY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; 